# Firmware-CLI superpowers → skills manifest
# Data, not code branches: each row maps a skill directory to its single
# source-of-truth playbook under ../../superpowers/. The sync_references
# script copies that playbook into <skill-dir>/reference/ so each skill is
# self-contained and portable while superpowers/ stays the one editing home.
#
# Format:  <skill-dir>   <source-playbook-filename>
#
superpowers-index          agent_index_START_HERE.md
superpowers-consistency    agent_consistency_playbook.md
superpowers-coding         agent_coding_playbook.md
superpowers-doc-sync       agent_doc_sync_playbook.md
superpowers-portability    agent_portability_playbook.md
superpowers-tool-docs      agent_script_doc_playbook.md
superpowers-spec-loop      spec_build_review_loop_playbook.md
